Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 天已经亮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快起床 爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 可不能迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是第一天上班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好啊 爱丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 玛莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的蔬菜怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这块地方啊收成一直不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 定期航线的气球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡 听说你今天开始上班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给 贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,带着去吧
